A redesigned survey contains a list of 21 names with altered lengths recorded as follows:
- 6 names of 4 letters each;
- 4 names of 5 letters each;
- 1 name of 6 letters;
- 5 names of 7 letters;
- 5 names of 8 letters.
What is the median length of these names?
**$\textbf{(A) }4\qquad\textbf{(B) }5\qquad\textbf{(C) }6\qquad\textbf{(D) }7\qquad \textbf{(E) }8$**
